      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay i get the pressure part now. so if it's a bug or ice, it's just a physical obstruction. what actually happens to the needle on the gauge if the pitot tube is blocked but the static port is still clear? does it just drop to zero or something?",
      "source": "evaluator"
